genericMethods

Class Equals

  • java.lang.Object
    • genericMethods.Equals

  • public class Equals
extends java.lang.Object
    A demonstration of a generic method. This class defines a (rather superfluous) static method that will test for equality (according to the equals() method!) of two objects of the same type.
    Version:
    October 2019
    Author:
    Hugh Osborne
